  "title": "Production Technician (up to $3100 gross + many OT + AWS, Tampines)",
  "description": "<p>✔ Up to $2700 (basic) + $300-400 (shift allowance) + $130 fixed allowance + Many OT + Bonuses</p><p>✔ Transport provided (to/fro)</p><p>✔ Best benefits in the market<br /></p><p><strong>Job Details</strong></p><p>• Working hours: 12 hours rotating shift (4-3-3-4, 8.30 to 8.45, monthly rotation)</p><p>• Location: Tampines</p><p>• Salary: Up to $2700 (basic) + $300-400 (shift allowance) + $130 fixed allowance + Many OT + Bonuses<br /></p><p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p><p>• Operating production machines and carry out production measurements</p><p>• Perform visual inspection and data entry of information</p><p>• Preparation of raw materials</p><p>• Perform inventory monitoring</p><p>• Update daily downtime and monitor production yield</p><p>• Involve in all production related activities in production floor</p><p>• Perform any other ad hoc duties as and when assigned<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>• Minimum Nitec/Diploma in Mechanical / Electrical Technology</p><p>• Must be able to perform OT & Rotating shifts in Cleanroom Environment<br /></p><p><strong>*To apply, attach your CV/Resume and apply in the link with your reason(s) for leaving past employments, last drawn and expected salary.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated with strictest confidentiality. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Thank you.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>RecruitFirst Pte Ltd E.A. 13C6342</strong></p><p><strong>Joseph Yap Shi Hao (R1767577)</strong></p>",
